description: I met two boys on the way to a quick lunch. One of them looked very promising so I offered them to pay the bill in exchange of a small interview. Unfortunately, the guy I was after was a bit shy or maybe he didn´t trust me, while the other one was extremely talkative. It took some time to get rid off him so I could continue with the cute one. The garages were full of people, we couldn´t do much there. So eventually we went to a hotel room to finish the job. The boy liked money very much. He didn´t want to talk about his occupation but mentioned occasional modeling jobs. That was good news. Models are usually not afraid to show their beautiful bodies. This one definitely wasn´t. After all, I was paying him serious money.
title: Czech Hunter 279
